public class BasicTileCacheMosaicer
extends Object
implements TileCacheMosaicer

BasicTileCacheMosaicer RasterServerBackedMosaicer is used to compose a destination raster using matching tiles in the tile cache, or if tiles are missing, will first try to create tile on-the-fly from higher resolution (descendant) tiles, or , if descendant tiles not found, from lower resolution (ancestor) tile
